org.treetank.utils
Class IConstants

java.lang.Object
  org.treetank.utils.IConstants

public final class IConstants
extends Object

IConstants

Interface to hold all constants of the node layer. The node kinds are equivalent to DOM node kinds for interoperability with saxon.
